{"tid":1931500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南海風雲】美海軍偵察機逼近香港 傳前往南海收集情報","createTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T10:47:32.000Z","uid":73092,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8a328dd9217317c34b78c7adec1ef39f5aefe9","tid":1931500,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"美國太平洋艦隊公佈，「羅斯福號」航空母艦（USS Theodore Roosevelt，CVN-71）及其戰鬥群，與兩棲攻擊艦「美利堅號」（USS America，LHA-6）的遠征戰鬥群（Expeditionary Strike Groups），15日起在南中國海進行演習。監察空軍動向的Twitter賬號「飛機守望」（Aircraft Spots）今日發佈兩張飛行路線圖顯示，美國海軍EP-3E「白羊座電子偵察機」穿過高雄對落的巴士海峽，再飛到接近香港的上空。根據相片比例顯示，偵察機與香港距離約100至150公里。目前，未知美軍的用意，以及解放軍有否派出軍機進行監視。<br />\n<br />\n內地微博消息稱，3月18日早晨，美海軍一架編號為159893，呼號為SF925的EP-3E「白羊座電子偵察機」，從日本嘉手納基地起飛，飛越巴士海峽前往南海實施情報偵察，飛行高度6,553米。<br />\n<br />\n美國太平洋艦隊15日在Twitter上公佈，兩個海軍艦艇編隊在南海進行演習，未有透露具體的演習項目，只公開多張艦艇航行的照片。據報，美軍兩個艦隊，代表着美軍第五代戰鬥火力，無可匹敵，按照以往慣例，美軍在南海進行這樣重大的軍演，解放軍均會出動強大海軍編隊到場，但不知是否新冠病毒疫情關係，解放軍南部戰區的海軍航空團，只出動兩架遠程轟炸機、兩架護航戰機，以及一架預警機到南海，同時出動054A型導彈護衞艦監視。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecad448580dd65afeedee6a478fe75b48527a98e","tid":1931500,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:28.000Z","msg":"第七艦隊"},{"pid":"ee923b8fb57674aafab21411ac70c7ca53cdb11b","tid":1931500,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:49.000Z","msg":"【教學】如何為美軍帶路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1871828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1871828</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"10f2c41c15b2d50eb753a287104021f9048828b9","tid":1931500,"uid":36481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:55.000Z","msg":"美軍來了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cf2d371d1142bbf7606db95cae62c80a287322","tid":1931500,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200318&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60727054\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200318%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60727054&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFyq0XD4M5CHb8byFtBYuAsM%3D&h=609af8c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200318%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60727054&h=bdf23de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200318&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60727054</a>"},{"pid":"4a8a5574310a1be72cb4eba29b236b77479937e1","tid":1931500,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07358985352ea3918dfc1e3ba4196273e3e872ab","tid":1931500,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b6557387abbb0bfb09187751e1dff561fd79eb","tid":1931500,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"sir this way <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUSA  USA  USA <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8f7eb828beb7531f453